# dwm-crack 

My personal build of the dynamic window manager (dwm) for Arch Linux. 
Customized for performance and a minimal aesthetic.

##  Preview
![Desktop Screenshot](screenshots/desktop.png)
*(Note: Create a 'screenshots' folder and put an image there later!)*

## 🛠️ Requirements
To build this, you need the Xlib header files and a few extra tools:
* `libx11`
* `libxft`
* `imlib2` (if using certain patches)
* `dmenu` (for the app launcher)

## 🚀 Installation
```bash
git clone [https://github.com/CrackBullet/dwm-crack.git](https://github.com/CrackBullet/dwm-crack.git)
cd dwm-crack
sudo make clean install
